es. We demonstrate the\ncapabilities of the Si:H GAP by creating models of hydrogenated liquid and\namorphous silicon, and showing that their energies, forces and stresses are in\nexcellent agreement with DFT results, and their structure as captured by bond\nand angle distributions, with both DFT and experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 19:05:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2021 23:42:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Jan 2022 00:55:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-07"}
