ly affected by\nintermittency in the MRI turbulence. We also discuss the potential of\naccelerating PeV cosmic-rays in hot accretion flows around supermassive black\nholes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jun 2021 11:53:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
