ized\nbentness of the dual of generalized bent functions and the bentness of the dual\nof bent functions, as well as the self-duality relations between generalized\nbent functions and bent functions by the decomposition of generalized bent\nfunctions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jun 2021 12:16:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
